						<ul>
							<li><a href="https://kakawachocolates.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Kakawa Chocolate House</strong></a>: {{{__ 'We never leave Santa Fe without stopping by Kakawa! This local favorite is a specialty chocolate shop with recipes that harken back to 1,000 BC. Try their truffles, caramels, hot chocolate mixes, renowned chocolate-dipped chile pods &mdash; and the best iced mochas, ever.'}}}</li>
						  <li><a href="http://www.dulcebakery.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Dulce Bakery</strong></a>: {{{__ 'Try their Mexican wedding cookies.'}}}</li>
						  <li><a href="https://www.lalecherianm.com/" target="_blank"><strong>La Lecheria</strong></a>: {{{__ 'An ice-cream shop known for unique flavor combinations and local ingredients.'}}}</li>
						</ul><br/>
